{"type":"article","id":22215,"title":"吉林省公安厅党委副书记、常务副厅长对人类文明做出的巨大贡献：《平安经》","uid":3685,"topics":[2030,217,1712,455],"contents":"日前，吉林省公安厅党委副书记、常务副厅长贺电所著《平安经》一书在网上引发讨论。据了解，该书全文以以“XXX平安”造句，吉林省应急管理厅微信公号在4月9日曾转发该书并称赞值得一读。《平安经》作为跨国传世的经类大作力作，是人类历史上仅见的首部平安经书，当永世流传。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWfiYWsAMxjf0?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWfiYWsAMxjf0?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWfiYWsAMxjf0?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWgOtXYAA3Sld?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWgOtXYAA3Sld?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWgOtXYAA3Sld?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWhbFWoAANBCk?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWhbFWoAANBCk?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWhbFWoAANBCk?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWimVWoAEex43?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWimVWoAEex43?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EeAWimVWoAEex43?format=jpg&amp;name=orig\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-07-28","agreeCount":9,"discussionCount":0}